lines.text:
[Standing inside jail against the word IT]
I was up against IT.
[Carries the word ON over his back]

[to Noah Webster]
Whats the matter does the cat got your tounge?
[Cat is shown in heaven holding a tounge]
[Sits with a man who is red full with anger]
Everytime I talked I would put my foot in my mouth. The judge pumped me up and he sent me up the river.
I was born with a silver spoon in my mouth.
[the Hipster's first remark to Noah Webster]
Outside it was raining cats and dogs.
